data.description: Welcome to this picturesque country charmer! This enchanting four-bedroom, two-bath residence rests on a sprawling one and a half acres of land, offering a tranquil oasis that combines rural serenity with convenient proximity to town and schools. Nestled amongst the natural beauty, this home boasts a two-car detached garage, providing ample space for vehicles and storage. With its inviting charm, spacious layout, and ideal location, this property truly embodies the essence of comfortable country living, while remaining just a stone's throw away from essential amenities. Your dream of a peaceful yet accessible lifestyle starts here.
